MIDI-Segment - a means to segment MIDI by equal duration

this module can be installed using cpanm:

    cpanm MIDI::Segment

run perldoc(1) on MIDI::Segment for documentation


to author a new release:

    perl Build.PL
    RELEASE_TESTING=1 ./Build test
    ./Build testcover
    ./Build disttest
    git tag -u ... -s v...
    ./Build dist
    cpan-upload ...
    git push ...
    ./Build realclean
